OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772885578
OL,3,CResolving police file redactions 'key'
OL,4,Cfor progress, Katie Simpson inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FResolving redactions in police
OL,8,Fmaterials is "key to unlocking future
OL,9,Fprogress", the inquest investigating
OL,10,Fthe death of showjumper Katie Simpson
OL,11,Fhas heard.
OL,13,FMs Simpson, 21, from Tynan, Co Armagh,
OL,14,Fdied at Altnagelvin Hospital in
OL,15,FLondonderry almost a week after an
OL,16,Fincident in Gortnessy Meadows,
OL,17,FLettershandoney, Co Derry, on August 3
OL,18,F2020.
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
