FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772885578
OL,3,CResolving police file redactions 'key'
OL,4,Cfor progress, Katie Simpson inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FPolice originally thought it was a
OL,8,Fsuicide, but the following year
OL,9,FJonathan Creswell, the partner of Ms
OL,10,FSimpson's sister, was arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,13,FThe trial of Creswell, 36, for murder
OL,14,Fended in April last year after his
OL,15,Fsudden death.
OL,17,FMs Simpson's death is due to be
OL,18,Fexamined at an inquest by coroner Joe
OL,19,FMcCrisken.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
