PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772885578
OL,3,CResolving police file redactions 'key'
OL,4,Cfor progress, Katie Simpson inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA pre-inquest review last year heard
OL,8,Fthere were 352 police files to be
OL,9,Fexamined, with between 25,000 and
OL,10,F29,000 pages, including 44 police
OL,11,Freports, 77 transmission files, a list
OL,12,Fof 165 exhibits, 237 statements and 53
OL,13,Finterview files.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772885578
OL,3,CResolving police file redactions 'key'
OL,4,Cfor progress, Katie Simpson inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FPhilip Henry KC, legal counsel to the
OL,8,Fcoroner, said there is an "issue
OL,9,Farising from the Sexual Offences Act
OL,10,F1992" that had been flagged to them by
OL,11,Fpolice and that Mr McCrisken had ruled
OL,12,Fthat his counsel should attempt to
OL,13,Fcontact people named as potential
OL,14,Fvictims of sexual offences.
OL,16,FMr Henry said they had been able to
OL,17,Fmake contact with "some of those
OL,18,Findividuals... but not all".
OL,26,@pD@[OUrD@EO]yD@SOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772885578
OL,3,CResolving police file redactions 'key'
OL,4,Cfor progress, Katie Simpson inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe told the inquest on Friday: "It's
OL,8,Fmy respectful submission to you, sir,
OL,9,Fthat you can't finalise any ruling on
OL,10,Fthis redaction issue until either
OL,11,Fyou've heard back from all, or
OL,12,Fexhausted reasonable efforts to make
OL,13,Fcontact with them all.
OL,15,F"I really see that as the key to
OL,16,Funlocking future progress because
OL,17,Funtil the redaction issue is resolved,
OL,18,Fthe redactions of the police material
OL,19,Fwhich will form the bulk of the
OL,20,Finquest papers, that can't be
OL,21,Ffinalised."
OL,26,@oD@`OUwD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772885578
OL,3,CResolving police file redactions 'key'
OL,4,Cfor progress, Katie Simpson inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Henry added: "We have a couple of
OL,8,Fapplications pending which rely on
OL,9,Fproviding PIPs (properly interested
OL,10,Fpersons) with a significant amount of
OL,11,Fdisclosure."
OL,13,FHe said his legal team has reviewed
OL,14,Fsensitive materials that are
OL,15,Fpotentially relevant to the inquest
OL,16,Fand the PSNI will be able to review.
OL,26,@oD@QOUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
