PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772885578
OL,3,CResolving police file redactions 'key'
OL,4,Cfor progress, Katie Simpson inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMark Robinson KC, representing the
OL,8,FPSNI, said there is not a "large
OL,9,Famount of documentation" but there are
OL,10,F"sensitivities" included, and gave a
OL,11,Ftimeline of eight weeks for the
OL,12,Fmarking-up process.
OL,14,FThe next pre-inquest review hearing
OL,15,Fwas scheduled for the second week of
OL,16,FMay.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
